data.description:
Welcome to your new home with a HUGE back yard! 
You can not get enough yard space on a recently built home. This home has it!
This home offers an open floor plan with an office, guest room and full bath dowstairs. Upstairs you will find a game room, owner's suit and two secondary rooms with a shared bath. Refrigerator will convey with property.
Did I mention the back yard?!
